\SM[double]\SE\SE[21]Wow... Today's meal is so luxurious...!
\SE[21]It's incredibly delicious too...!

\SM[nod]\SE[4]Yeah, Lunaroa got too excited and bought a lot of
fresh ingredients. \SE[3]If we don't use them up, they'll go
bad...

\SE[29]Ahaha... Lunaroa is such a mischievous person...
\SE[91]But, really... It's delicious...!

\SE[4]Lunaroa, make sure you eat too, okay? [1]You have to take
responsibility for buying too much.

\SE\SM[nod]\SE[45]Oh, I forgot to eat... \SE[0]That's right,
since we have them... \SM[nod]\SE[45]Let's eat while using Laura
as a side dish...

\SE[46] (Ah... Laura, who is devouring her meal so eagerly...
\SE[47] It's so endearing... and somehow 'sensual'... \SE[35]
When I die, I want to be 'digested' by Laura and die...)

\SE[74]I've already given up. \.I'm tired today, so I'm going to
sleep now.... \!\SE[51]I'm sorry, but please manage without
me....

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending time
here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while
studying... so she ends up going to the bathroom... quite
frequently...
